      • getAggTrades

        void getAggTrades(String symbol,
                  String fromId,
                  Integer limit,
                  Long startTime,
                  Long endTime,
                  BinanceApiCallback<List<AggTrade>> callback)
        Get compressed, aggregate trades. Trades that fill at the time, from the same order, with the same price will have the quantity aggregated. If both startTime and endTime are sent, limitshould not be sent AND the distance between startTime and endTime must be less than 24 hours.
        Parameters:
        symbol - symbol to aggregate (mandatory)
        fromId - ID to get aggregate trades from INCLUSIVE (optional)
        limit - Default 500; max 1000 (optional)
        startTime - Timestamp in ms to get aggregate trades from INCLUSIVE (optional).
        endTime - Timestamp in ms to get aggregate trades until INCLUSIVE (optional).
        callback - the callback that handles the response

      • getAggTrades

      • getCandlestickBars

        void getCandlestickBars(String symbol,
                        CandlestickInterval interval,
                        Integer limit,
                        Long startTime,
                        Long endTime,
                        BinanceApiCallback<List<Candlestick>> callback)
        Kline/candlestick bars for a symbol. Klines are uniquely identified by their open time.
        Parameters:
        symbol - symbol to aggregate (mandatory)
        interval - candlestick interval (mandatory)
        limit - Default 500; max 1000 (optional)
        startTime - Timestamp in ms to get candlestick bars from INCLUSIVE (optional).
        endTime - Timestamp in ms to get candlestick bars until INCLUSIVE (optional).
        callback - the callback that handles the response containing a candlestick bar for the given symbol and interval
